# Images & Media

## Storefront

- Product cards: 1:1 or 4:5 · Blog thumbs: 16:9 · Hero: full-bleed intentional crop
- Warm soft lighting; real product/context — not abstract purple gradients
- Use `next/image`; set width/height or fill + sized parent
- Priority only on true LCP hero
- Lazy-load below fold

## Platform

- Bytes in S3-compatible storage; DB stores metadata only
- Validate MIME/size; private assets via signed URLs
- Don’t store binaries in Postgres
- Generate variants via BullMQ jobs when needed (thumb/web)

Empty alt only when decorative; products need descriptive alt (name + key trait).
